    81| * surface (Profile administration, Admin Panel guard, OwnerOnly gate) derives
    82| * from this so there is exactly one owner-access decision, never duplicated
    83| * per-screen booleans that drift out of sync.
    84| *
    85| * Owner access is granted when any of these hold:
    86| * - open-access build mode is enabled (login bypassed in this build)
